[I] Qt 5 addon providing access to numerous types of archives

[T] KArchive provides classes for easy reading, creation and manipulation of
[T] "archive" formats like ZIP and TAR. It also provides transparent
[T] compression and decompression of data, like the GZip format, via a subclass
[T] of QIODevice.

[U] https://www.kde.org

